OL,7,FThe UK Envoy for Post Holocaust Issues
OL,8,Fwill address Guernsey's Jewish
OL,9,Fcommunity this afternoon (13 February)
OL,10,Fas his report into Alderney deaths
OL,11,Fduring Nazi occupation nears its
OL,12,Fconclusion.
OL,14,FLord Eric Pickles will host a dinner
OL,15,Fat the Old Government House Hotel at
OL,16,F7pm to share his views regarding
OL,17,FGuernsey, past and present.
