OL,7,FIn 1941, Nazi occupiers built four
OL,8,Flabour camps on the island, with
OL,9,Fprisoners forced to build the island's
OL,10,Ffortifications including bunkers,
OL,11,Ftunnels, and air raid shelters.
OL,13,FLord Pickles has appointed 11
OL,14,Findependent experts to examine
OL,15,Fevidence to dispel speculation over
OL,16,Fthe number of deaths.
